# Python-generated files
__pycache__/
*.py[oc]
build/
dist/
wheels/
*.egg-info

# Virtual environments
.venv

# coverage artifacts (regenerated by tests; never track)
coverage.out
coverage.out.tmp

# generated protobuf bindings — never committed; run `task generate` (buf) to
# produce them locally from the vendored proto/ (source of truth: kafka-svc).
# gen/* (not gen/) so a single subtree can be re-included below: the Go bindings
# stay ignored, but the Rust contracts crate is committed.
gen/*

# EXCEPTION: the gen/rust serde crate IS committed. The tiny-monitor widget consumes it
# as a path/git dependency and does NOT regenerate it (it has no buf/protoc toolchain), so
# the checked-in tree is the source of truth for the widget. Only its build output and the
# consumer-resolved lockfile stay ignored.
!gen/rust/
gen/rust/target/
gen/rust/Cargo.lock

# delightd runtime artifact
traefik.json
